item.title: Quick start
item.description: hello world # start writing code in hydra! to get started: Go to https://hydra.ojack.xyz Close the top window by clicking the [x] in the top right. Change some numbers Type “ctrl+shift+enter” to run the code (or use the triangle run button) have fun! there is no “wrong” way to code in hydra :] Next steps # For more a more in-depth introductions see Getting Started: video synth basics. For an overview of available guides and resources, see learning.
